data.description: Welcome to your dream home just minutes away from the serene lake! This stunning new construction boasts 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 luxurious bathrooms, offering the perfect blend of comfort and style. Step inside and be gretted by an open- concept floor plan, designed to maximize natural light and create a seamless flowthroughout the home.The living area is perfect for entertaining. Retreat to the master suite, a true oasis of relaxation. With its generous size. Two additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family members or guests, and a second full bathroom ensures everyone's comfort and convenience.  Don't miss this chance to make this exquisite new construction your forever home!
